{"title":"Workshop 01 - Introduction to ARBO-WATCH","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Workshop 01 - Introduction to ARBO-WATCH","date":"2024-03-01","facilitator":"Jane Doe","categories":["introduction","arboreal-monitoring"],"description":"An introduction to the ARBO-WATCH project, its goals, and the monitoring framework."},"headingText":"About This Workshop","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n\nThis workshop introduces participants to the ARBO-WATCH project — its goals, structure, and the monitoring framework that underpins the 4-year programme. By the end of this workshop, participants will understand the field and data workflows used throughout the series.\n\n---\n\n## Prerequisites\n\nBefore attending, please ensure you have:\n\n- Installed [R](https://cran.r-project.org/) (version ≥ 4.2) and [RStudio](https://posit.co/download/rstudio-desktop/)\n- Installed the `tidyverse` package: `install.packages(\"tidyverse\")`\n- Read the project background document (see Materials below)\n- Brought a laptop with at least 4 GB of free disk space\n\n---\n\n## Timetable\n\n| Day | Date | Topics | Facilitator |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| [Day 1](day-01.qmd) | 01 Mar 2024 | Welcome, Project Overview, Intro to Arboreal Monitoring | Jane Doe |\n| [Day 2](day-02.qmd) | 02 Mar 2024 | Monitoring Protocols, Deep Dive, Group Discussion | Jane Doe, Maria Lopez |\n\n---\n\n## Materials\n\n### Slides\n\n| Day | Link |\n|---|---|\n| Day 1 | [View Slides](slides.qmd){.btn .btn-sm .btn-primary} |\n| Day 2 | [View Slides](slides.qmd){.btn .btn-sm .btn-primary} |\n\n### R Scripts\n\n| File | Description |\n|---|---|\n| [analysis.R](analysis.R) | Workshop 01 R script |\n\n### Reference Documents\n\n| File | Description |\n|---|---|\n| [reference.pdf](reference.pdf) | Background reading for Workshop 01 |\n\n\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n## About This Workshop\n\nThis workshop introduces participants to the ARBO-WATCH project — its goals, structure, and the monitoring framework that underpins the 4-year 